## Anti-Patterns

- Hardcoded Supabase table shapes — use `DatabaseDTOs.ts` and mappers
- Monetization UI with free-form prices
- Graph validation only in UI — use `AnalysisService`
- Schema changes only in `web/` — migrations go to umbrella `supabase/migrations/`

